			<h1 class="centered">Hi, I'm James.</h1>
			<p>I'm the Co-founder & CEO of
			<%=link_to("Teleborder", "https://www.teleborder.com", :target => "_blank", :id => "teleborder-site-link")%>. Teleborder helps companies hire, manage, and retain international employees. Our investors include Khosla Ventures, Recruit, IDG, and Y Combinator (S13). You can read more about us 
			<%=link_to("here", "http://www.forbes.com/sites/adrianagardella/2015/04/22/a-tech-company-seeks-to-ease-employers-immigration-hassles/", :target => "_blank", :id => "first-press-link")%>,
