			<%=link_to("Forbes 30 Under 30", "http://www.forbes.com/sites/danielfisher/2015/01/05/white-house-officials-legal-entrepreneurs-dominate-30-under-30-law-and-policy-list/", :target => "_blank", :id => "forbes-3030-link")%> for Law and Policy.</p>
